## 🚀 How to Run

1. **Clone this repository**  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/Automated-Data-Quality-Check.git
   cd Automated-Data-Quality-Check/scripts

2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the script
python data_quality_check.py

4. Check the output
The report will be saved in the reports/ folder as:
data_quality_report.xlsx
